{"word":"ὑποζώννυμι","slug":"ὑποζώννυμι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὑποζώννυμι</b></el> <el>(and <el>-ύω</el>) (<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-ζώσω</el>) (<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <el>ὑπ-έζωσμαι</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to undergird</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>ζειρὰς ὑπεζωσμένοι</el> <i>girt</i> with <el>ζειραί</el>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to undergird</i> or <i>frap</i> a ship (<a href='S:vide'>v.</a> <a href='S:ὑπόζωμα'><el>ὑπόζωμα</el></a> II), <b><a href='S:Polybius'>Polyb.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}